At Uni Systems, we are working towards turning digital visions into reality. We are continuously growing and we are looking for a Solutions Architect to join our UniQue team.
What will you be doing in this role?
Design the Service Oriented Architecture (SOA) tier;
Participate in design sessions with project staff as required;
Build business processes to support orchestration of web services;
